'''Amory Lorch''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by [[Fintan McKeown]] and debuts in &quot;[[What is Dead May Never Die]].&quot; Ser Amory Lorch is a knight fighting for [[House Lannister]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]]. He was killed by [[Jaqen H'ghar]] at [[Harrenhal]].

